==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Joyance
<hw>Joy"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>joiance</ets>.]</ety> <def>Enjoyment; gayety; festivity;
joyfulness.</def> <rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some days of <qex>joyance</qex> are decreed to all.</q>
<rj><qau>Byron.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>From what hid fountains doth thy <qex>joyance</qex> flow?</q>
<rj><qau>Trench.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Joyancy</ent>⟦br⟧
